For Eid al-Adha, I joined hands with @petaindia and @Serveneedy to donate vegan biryani to 1,000 people in need in Hyderabad. Everyone enjoyed a delicious, nourishing meal—no harm done.
 
Eid is about giving back to the society in a compassionate way.
 
Let’s honour the true spirit of Eid—with kindness that saves lives.
